(4, 'Blade of the Ruined King', 3200, NULL, 'Unique – Mist\'s Edge: Basic attacks deal bonus physical damage on-hit equal to (Melee role 8% / Ranged role 5%) of the target\'s current health, with a maximum of 100 against Minion icon minions and Monster icon monsters.\r\nUnique – Clawing Shadows: Basic attacks on-hit against enemy champions apply a stack for 6 seconds, stacking up to 3 times. The third stack consumes them all to Slow icon slow the target by 30% for 1 second (15 second cooldown).', 'Blade_of_the_Ruined_King_item_HD.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 25, 40, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
